---
import Button from "./Button.astro";
---

<section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-[40px] mt-[60px] md:mt-[100px] mb-[60px] md:mb-[100px]">
  <div class="bg-pink rounded-[6px] px-6 md:px-[60px] lg:px-[115px] py-[40px] md:py-[76px] text-center">
    <h2 class="font-tight text-[36px] md:text-[64px] lg:text-[96px] leading-[1.1] uppercase text-dark mb-[40px] md:mb-[105px]">
      Give your KiwiSaver a proper once-over.
    </h2>
    <p class="font-tight text-[22px] md:text-[36px] lg:text-[48px] leading-[1.15] uppercase text-dark max-w-[1130px] mx-auto mb-[40px] md:mb-[80px]">
      It does not need to be complicated, and it does not need to take forever. A quick check now could help you feel a whole lot clearer about what you have and what to do next.
    </p>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6 md:gap-[100px]">
      <Button label="CHECK MY FUND" href="#health-check" />
      <!-- Center icon -->
      <img src="/icon.svg" alt="Prosper" class="w-[48px] h-[36px] md:w-[64px] md:h-[48px] hidden md:block" />
      <Button label="BOOK A REVIEW" href="#book" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
